title: These Foos on Forming a Latino YouTube Group, Onlyfans, Brand Deals & More
description:
These Foos talk about being inspired by Doknow, their come up, what they have in the works and more!

-----
00:00 Intro
6:23 Brian sold fake SBs to Flex
10:03 "All the bad Valley b*tches fill up the tank every weekend"
11:55 The group became "These Foos officially" during their Doknow interview, it was actually inspired by Doknow
13:03 Doknow wishes they didn't have girlfriends so they could get it crackin on OF and live like rock stars for a bit before settling down
13:16 Actually, Phil and Flex do have an OF account! This is exclusive, they never mentioned it before
15:00 Some pages already licked their nudes! Plus, apparently, they're going CRAZY on there! 
20:25 Trying to find real content ideas for videos is hard
22:04 Not marketable if you're from the hood? There are ways to go around to get a mainstream appeal
23:00 Landing one of their first deal ever with Plug Play
24:24 Thinking long-term and doing things that may prevent you from getting a big brand deal 
25:50 Some things they do because they are Latino, David Dobrick can do the same thing or even crazier, and get a deal 
30:45 These Foos working with Buzz Ballz they turned them down because they're latinos but they are targeting the Latin audience
36:29 Fashion Nova just reached out to Doknow!?!
42:57 How These Foos split the money? Making everything far for everyone
45:33 Brian almost left the group because of his girl
52:38 Getting their ___ eaten
53:45 Phil likes getting his ___ eaten with his legs up
